<p>It’s not supposed to be linezolid or any other real oxazolidinone antibiotic. It is supposed to be a fictional antibiotic in the same family, produced by an anomalous yeast. It was extraordinarily powerful and *unlike* actual oxazolidinone antibiotics such as linezolid, devoid of substantial side effects. In universe the chemical was identified and a mundane chemical synthesis devised, making it an -EX</p>
